# Shattered Pixel Dungeon Mod

## Project structure

- `core/` - Main game logic, assets, messages
- `SPD-classes/` - Upstream libGDX/SPD base classes (avoid editing)
- `desktop/` - Desktop launcher, streaming server
- `android/` - Android build

## Key files for common changes

- **Settings**: `SPDSettings.java` (keys + get/set), `WndSettings.java` (UI), `windows.properties` (strings)
- **UI components**: `core/.../ui/`
- **Actors/mobs**: `core/.../actors/`

## Conventions

- Follow existing SPD style: package `com.shatteredpixel.shatteredpixeldungeon.*`
- Add new settings via `SPDSettings` + `WndSettings` + `windows.properties`
- Use `Messages.get()` for user-facing text; add keys to `*.properties` in `core/src/main/assets/messages/`
